樣嘢...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中國共產黨都未有就開始等 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b25576554503c5b55cef2eb9181244aea6de1bb","tid":308262,"uid":9171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T05:20:54.000Z","msg":"唔衝？"},{"pid":"10497e002d4e51ab07015170e87b8c8756a838ad","tid":308262,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T05:22:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你們是飯桶！對不起我們，我們等得很久，甚麼都沒有&hellip;&hellip;他媽的！（派飛）比小便更快完&hellip;&hellip;<span style=\"color: red;\">我等咗百幾年啦。</span>」<br />\n清朝人都黎參觀遼寧號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n甲午戰爭 定遠號d人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1b4fc9cfc902d1bfb447577226a9270a13905e5","tid":308262,"uid":14449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T05:28:31.000Z","msg":"上次睇俄佬戰艦又係全部廢佬，今次支那艦排得又係垃圾廢佬"},{"pid":"33660036f4553d30a553a36a27eb39f2ba373734","tid":308262,"uid":65481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T05:28:40.000Z","msg":"美國d航母，補給艦成日黎香港架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解個時唔去睇<br />\n中國d艦好日都唔黎一次<br />\n做咩要去同人逼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"110f9d59b0e5e3bd387d24a5fb28cc6dc1c1f877","tid":308262,"uid":103355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T05:48:05.000Z","msg":"部垃圾船都好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />實戰起上黎分分鐘比人多靶射<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a41ac30b0ece6ff3c5a0acee4c5072835f249ead","tid":308262,"uid":5547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T05:57:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上次睇俄佬戰艦又係全部廢佬，今次支那艦排得又係垃圾廢佬</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n全你老母"},{"pid":"80fdd2a6cda1180b1027ba0c23b745aa80d87959","tid":308262,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T06:01:36.000Z","msg":"我支持即場處決班廢老<br />\n班大陸閪仆心仆命黎保護你班濕鳩<br />\n唔跪低謝xi隆恩重屌人？"},{"pid":"b94ad189ae1d4b28386d36ec5ec7ceb3447d35c5","tid":308262,"uid":70429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T06:01:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>肯定收左美國錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 曲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n曲你老味咩"},{"pid":"e3addd4d264e4411fc9da22d1eb6efc77c23bebe","tid":308262,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T06:02:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}